f the stellar evolution, NS or WD, they recover the initial value of\n\\Gamma(M, EOS) ~ 0.4 acquired at the PMS. Finally, we have introduced a\nmacroscopic stability \"criterion\" for neutron star models based on the\nproperties of the relativistic product \\alpha\\beta_{GR}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Feb 2013 21:35:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Feb 2013 17:23:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 4 Mar 2013 15:32:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-06-04"}
